data.description: Highly motivated seller offering a turn-key ready, meticulously remodeled residence in a charming OVERSIZED cul-de-sac lot, backing to a greenbelt w/ NO rear neighbors. Inside showcases an open layout adorned w/ NEW floors(no carpet), NEW bath vanities, NEW lighting/ceiling fans & NEW HVAC system. An inviting office space & an open formal dining area adorned w/ lofty ceilings & stunning archways flows into the spacious living room w/ fireplace. The updated kitchen boasts quartz counters, ample storage & NEW dishwasher. The 1st level primary exudes sophistication w/ tray ceilings & updated en-suite bath, while upstairs offers a game room, 3 bedrooms, & an updated bath. The vast, fully fenced backyard presents endless possibilities, accompanied by a BRAND NEW fence, awaiting your personal touch into the oasis of your dreams. Plus! Community amenities including a dog park, fitness park, pool, tennis courts, & elementary school, along w/ Kroger, Starbucks, & much more just moments away.
